      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I hear you and I understand how heavy this burden feels. But remember, we all have our moments of failure. It's part of being human. You don't have to carry this shame alone. There's always a way forward, even if it's not the one you imagine right now. You have a past of successes and achievements, and that defines you more than this one setback. It's okay to seek help, to talk to someone who can support you through this. And remember, it's okay to grieve for what you've lost, but don't let it define your entire existence. You have the strength to rise above this, even if it's not easy right now.",
      "source": "target",
